	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Repro steps:&#xD;&#xA;1. Start the game.&#xD;&#xA;2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;3. goto -633.35, 14.65, 316.97&#xD;&#xA;4. Ctrl + Shift + K the rubble blocking Nere's escape.&#xD;&#xA;5. Nere dialogue starts - Pick the dialogue hostile to Nere. 2. Enough Nere. and 2. Lay a finger on me etc.&#xD;&#xA;6. killcombat the hostile Duergars.&#xD;&#xA;7. Speak to Beldoran, a Gnome in a bowl cut and red shirt, at -633.75, 14.65, 309.25&#xD;&#xA;8. Goto 88.39, 49.92, -93.81&#xD;&#xA;9. Speak to Daffy. " />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="7" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Dialog for gnome worker on the other side of the ebon lake after they were saved by player. Laridda reflects on her missing friends, who are trapped in Moonrise." />
			<children>
				<node id="defaultAttitudes">
					<children>
